#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kreversi.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KReversi is a simple one player strategy game played against the computer. "
"If a player's piece is captured by an opposing player, that piece is turned "
"over to reveal the color of that player. A winner is declared when one "
"player has more pieces of his own color on the board and there are no more "
"possible moves."
msgstr ""
"KReversi er eit enkelt strategispel for éin spelar mot datamaskina. Når ein "
"spelar tek ei av brikkene til motstandaren, vert ho snudd slik at fargen til "
"spelaren vert synleg. Vinnaren vert kåra når ein spelar har flest brikker i "
"sin farge og det ikkje lenger finst nokon moglege trekk."
